// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// DPM package-project scaffold templates.
//
// Embeds the minimal dpk/dproj templates used to generate package projects for
// source-only libraries (dpm prepare, and auto-generation at install time for
// packages declaring `package definitions`). One copy is carried by every
// dpm.exe and DPM.IDE.*.dll binary so generation is fully self-contained.
//
// Linked by DPM.Core.Project.Prepare.Templates via `{$R}` directive — see that
// unit for the resource names the loader expects (DPM_DPK_TEMPLATE /
// DPM_DPROJ_TEMPLATE, type TEMPLATE).
//
// Update flow:
//   1. Edit templates\dpm-package.dpk.template / .dproj.template (CRLF, UTF-8).
//   2. Rebuild — Delphi compiles this .rc via brcc32 on demand.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

DPM_DPK_TEMPLATE   TEMPLATE "templates\dpm-package.dpk.template"
DPM_DPROJ_TEMPLATE TEMPLATE "templates\dpm-package.dproj.template"
